HERS data example

hers.Rd

This dataset contains data from the HERS study used for demonstration purposes. Missing data (7-8%) has been omitted.

Usage

hers

Format

A data frame with n rows and p variables:

age

age in years

bmi

BMI (kg/m^2)

dbp

diastolic blood pressure.

diabetes

diabetes

dmpills

oral DM medication by self-report

drinkany

any current alcohol consumption

exercise

exercise at least 3 times per week.

globrat

self-reported health

glucose

fasting glucose (mg/dl)

hdl

HDL cholesterol (mg/dl)

hdl1

year 1 HDL cholesterol (mg/dl).

ht

random assignment to hormone therapy

htnmeds

anti-hypertensive use

insulin

insulin use by self-report

ldl

LDL cholesterol (mg/dl)

medcond

other serious conditions by self-report.

physact

comparative physical activity.

raceth

race/ethnicity.

sbp

systolic blood pressure

smoking

current smoker

statins

statin use

tg

triglycerides (mg/dl)

waist

waist (cm).

weight

weight (kg)

whr

waist/hip ratio.

Source

hers
